                            lobe</tp:descriptive-statement-part></tp:descriptive-statement-part></tp:descriptive-statement>
                ...</p>
        </tp:treatment-sec>
        <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="Biology-Ecology">
            <title>Habitat</title>
            <p><tp:taxon-name>S. zero</tp:taxon-name>
                <tp:descriptive-statement content-type="trait">occurs in wetland and swampy sides,
                    in plant debris and mosses among tussocks (Eskov 1988; Tanasevitch 2006, 2008),
                    in floodplain forests (Marusik 2005) and spruce fir and mixed forests (Marusik
                    et al. 2007)</tp:descriptive-statement>. </p>
        </tp:treatment-sec>
    </tp:treatment-sec>
